{"tid":2077923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息指本港增至少12輸入個案 主要由巴基斯坦來港","createTime":"2020-06-24T15:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T01:33:48.000Z","uid":133159,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"669e151812041277a29351ef1887c94e804090d9","tid":2077923,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"消息指，本港今日晚上再新增至少12宗確診個案，均屬輸入個案，主要由巴基斯坦來港。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心下午公布，截至今日下午4時，中心正調查兩宗新增2019冠狀病毒病確診個案，至今本港個案累計1 180宗（包括1 179宗確診個案和一宗疑似個案）。今日公布的新增個案涉及一男一女，年齡分別為55及47歲，他們曾於潛伏期身處菲律賓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係仆你個街<br />\n呢兩個禮拜多咗成百個確診患者<br />\n全部都係巴基斯坦<br />\n<br />\n識人喺隔離中心做<br />\n班仆街巴基真喺痴撚線"},{"pid":"80b097d56783168473c47f35343e2cd59ee776fb","tid":2077923,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef05079f27ae62199a7276eba47ef8c2ae7742e0","tid":2077923,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af99d2b26925ce6e760b4bdfb6faf3000ec0b525","tid":2077923,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122ea06a8cbd00b6f0e64b9d21d8307faf0b2dee","tid":2077923,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"想問下接撚夠巴基爛坦未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無咁撚多人有香港身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56890b62318d5359d1426f63720bdab139022d29","tid":2077923,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"669e151812041277a29351ef1887c94e804090d9","tid":2077923,"u